INNER JOIN [Common].[QuestionBank] AS [qb] ON [gq].[QuestionId] = [qb].[QuestionId]
WHERE [gq].[JobId] = @__bodyModel_JobId_0
ORDER BY [qb].[QuestionId]

SELECT [eh].[EmploymentId], [eh].[CandidateId], [eh].[StartDate], CASE
    WHEN [eh].[IsCurrentJob] = 1
    THEN GETDATE() ELSE [eh].[EndDate]
END AS [EndDate], [eh].[Organization], [eh].[Designation], [eh].[IsCurrentJob]

09-Sep-2020 14:06:26.705 +06:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (122ms) [Parameters=[@__bodyModel_CandidateId_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__bodyModel_CompanyId_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__bodyModel_ApplicationId_2='?' (DbType = Int32), @__bodyModel_JobId_3='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT TOP(1) [c].[JobCategoryId] AS [CandidateJobCategoryId], [cat].[JobCategoryName] AS [CandidateJobCategoryName], [job].[JobCategoryId] AS [CompanyJobCategoryId], [jobcat].[JobCategoryName] AS [CompanyJobCategoryName], [job].[YearOfExperience] AS [JobYearOfExperience], [a].[MarkPercentage]
FROM [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [a]
INNER JOIN [Candidate].[Candidates] AS [c] ON [a].[CandidateId] = [c].[CandidateId]
INNER JOIN [Common].[JobCategory] AS [cat] ON [c].[JobCategoryId] = [cat].[JobCategoryId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Jobs] AS [job] ON [a].[JobId] = [job].[JobId]

INNER JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [aj] ON [j].[JobId] = [aj].[JobId]
INNER JOIN [Candidate].[Candidates] AS [c] ON [aj].[CandidateId] = [c].[CandidateId]
WHERE (([j].[CompanyId] = @__bodyModel_CompanyId_0) AND ([aj].[StatusId] = @__bodyModel_StatusId_1)) AND ([aj].[IsProfileView] = 0)
ORDER BY [aj].[ApplicationId] DESC

SELECT [j].[JobId], [j].[JobTitle], [aj].[TotalExamMarks], [aj].[ObtainMarks], [aj].[MarkPercentage], [aj].[CandidateId], [aj].[StatusId], [c].[CandidateName], [aj].[ApplicationId], [aj].[CompanyId], [aj].[IsProfileMatch], [aj].[IsProfileView]
FROM [Job].[Jobs] AS [j]

END AS [StatusId], CASE
    WHEN [aj].[ApplicationId] IS NULL
    THEN 0 ELSE [aj].[ApplicationId]
END AS [ApplicationId]

INNER JOIN [Common].[Districts] AS [d] ON [j].[JobLocation] = [d].[DistrictId]
INNER JOIN [Job].[Companies] AS [c] ON [j].[CompanyId] = [c].[CompanyId]
LEFT JOIN [Job].[AppliedJobs] AS [aj] ON [j].[JobId] = [aj].[JobId]
WHERE (([j].[JobId] = @__appliedJob_JobId_0) AND ([j].[IsActive] = 1)) AND ([aj].[CandidateId] = @__appliedJob_CandidateId_1)
